data.description: **PLEASE ENJOY THE 3D INTERACTIVE VIRTUAL TOUR ASSOCIATED WITH THIS LISTING – As you step inside, you will immediately be greeted by this immaculate mid-century modern interior that has been fully updated to meet your modern desires. This homes features  3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, plus an office! This stunning home offers ample space for you and your loved ones to thrive with an open floor plan and extended family room. The polished terrazzo floors, the gorgeous updated custom kitchen featuring quartz countertops, and BOSCH appliances will satisfy the most discerning home owner.  Each bathroom has been fully updated including kohler fixtures and the exterior was recently painted. The A/C was replaced 9/2023. This home is move in ready! This home is situated on just under a quarter of an acre with a large fenced in backyard with beautiful foliage in the heart of one of the most sought after neighborhoods in all of Sarasota.  Southgate is centrally located near Sarasota Memorial Hospital, Arlington Park, Downtown Sarasota, & Southside Village.  Plenty of extra parking or room for your new sparkling pool!
